//! Precomputed inverse-Vandermonde coefficients for **P3** nodal Lagrange bases on the reference
//! triangle `(0,0),(1,0),(0,1)` and tet `(0,0,0),(1,0,0),(0,1,0),(0,0,1)`.
//!
//! Nodes are the **degree-3 lattice**: integer barycentric weights `(i,j,k)/3` with `i+j+k=3`
//! (triangle) / `(d0,d1,d2,d3)/3` summing to 3 (tetrahedron).
//!
//! Monomial order (triangle): `1, x, y, x², xy, y², x³, x²y, xy², y³`.
//! Monomial exponents (tet): see [`TET_P3_EXP`] — total degree ≤ 3 in `(x,y,z)`.

// Generated by exact `Fraction` inversion; shape `k` is `phi_k = sum_m COEFF[m][k] * mono_m`.

